5630,"Khalid Tahan ne Husain se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur main Qasim ( taqseem karne wala ( bana kar bheja gaya hun, tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
5631,"Khalid Tahan ne Husain se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur main Qasim ( taqseem karne wala ( bana kar bheja gaya hun, tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
5632,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Saeed ashajj ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Aamash ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se hadis sunai unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere naam par naam rakho aur meri kunniyat par kunniyat na rakho, kyonke main hi abul-Qaasim hon tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun aur Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein hai : apni kunniyat na rakho."
5633,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Saeed ashajj ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Aamash ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se hadis sunai unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere naam par naam rakho aur meri kunniyat par kunniyat na rakho, kyonke main hi abul-Qaasim hon tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun aur Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein hai : apni kunniyat na rakho."
5634,abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : Qasim banaya gaya hun tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun.
5635,abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : Qasim banaya gaya hun tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun.
5636,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Muhammad-bin Bishr ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai unhon-ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Ansar mein se aik shakhs ke yahan ladka paida hua us ne uska naam Muhammad rakhna chaha to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur aap se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ansar ne achchha kya, mere naam par naam rakho, meri kunniyat par (apni ( kunniyat na rakho."
5637,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Muhammad-bin Bishr ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai unhon-ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Ansar mein se aik shakhs ke yahan ladka paida hua us ne uska naam Muhammad rakhna chaha to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur aap se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ansar ne achchha kya, mere naam par naam rakho, meri kunniyat par (apni ( kunniyat na rakho."
5638,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Musanna , Muhammad-bin Amr bin jabla aur Bishr bin Khalid ne Muhammad-bin-Jafar se. Muhammad-bin-Jafar, ibne-abi Adi aur Nazar-bin-Shumail ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada Mansoor Sulaiman aur Husain-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, jis tarah un sab ki riwayat hai, jinki hadis ham pahley bayan kar chukey hain, Shoba se nazar ki bayan ki hui hadis mein hai kaha : usmein Husain aur Sulaiman ne izafa kya, Husain ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey Qasim bana kar bheja gaya hai, main tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun. padhi. aur Sulaiman ne kaha : main hi Qasim hon, tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun."
5639,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Musanna , Muhammad-bin Amr bin jabla aur Bishr bin Khalid ne Muhammad-bin-Jafar se. Muhammad-bin-Jafar, ibne-abi Adi aur Nazar-bin-Shumail ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada Mansoor Sulaiman aur Husain-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, jis tarah un sab ki riwayat hai, jinki hadis ham pahley bayan kar chukey hain, Shoba se nazar ki bayan ki hui hadis mein hai kaha : usmein Husain aur Sulaiman ne izafa kya, Husain ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey Qasim bana kar bheja gaya hai, main tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun. padhi. aur Sulaiman ne kaha : main hi Qasim hon, tumharey darmyan taqseem karta hun."
5640,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha : hamein ( Muhammad (bin Munkadir ne hadis sunai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, ham mein se aik shakhs ke yahan aik ladka paida hua, us shakhs ne iska naam Qasim rakha, ham ne kaha : ham tumhen abul-Qaasim ki kunniyat se nahi pukaarengey. na (tumhari ye khahish poori karke) tumhari aankhen thandi karengey to wo shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye sab baat batai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum apne betey ka naam Abdur-Rehman rakh lo."
5641,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha : hamein ( Muhammad (bin Munkadir ne hadis sunai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, ham mein se aik shakhs ke yahan aik ladka paida hua, us shakhs ne iska naam Qasim rakha, ham ne kaha : ham tumhen abul-Qaasim ki kunniyat se nahi pukaarengey. na (tumhari ye khahish poori karke) tumhari aankhen thandi karengey to wo shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye sab baat batai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum apne betey ka naam Abdur-Rehman rakh lo."
5642,"Rooh bin-Qasim ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne ye alfaz nahi kahey : aur ham tumhari aankhen thandi nahi karengey."
5643,"Rooh bin-Qasim ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne ye alfaz nahi kahey : aur ham tumhari aankhen thandi nahi karengey."
5644,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Amr Naqid , Zuhair-bin-Harab , aur ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Sirin se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : abul-Qasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere naam par naam rakho aur meri kunniyat par kunniyat na rakho . Amr ne kaha Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha aur maine suna nahi kaha."
